{"title":"Blanks","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"drip-basics-sweatpants-f","title":"DRIP BASICS SWEATPANTS – F","description":"\u003cp\u003e420 GSM.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eCotton fleece fabric.\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eStraight baggy fit.\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eCombed \u0026amp; bio washed.\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eOnly for female.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eDesigned for ultimate comfort and effortless style.\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eStraight-fit joggers made from luxurious 350 GSM fabric.\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eOffers a soft feel and superior durability.\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eFeatures a convenient back pocket for added utility.\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eBlends practicality with everyday streetwear style.\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eSuitable for casual days or elevated street looks.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\nCare Guide\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eMachine wash the jogger inside out with like colors.\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eUse cold water to preserve the fabric’s quality.\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eTumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage.\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eStore the jogger in a cool, dry place to prevent moisture or mold buildup.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\nCore Features\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eJoggers with 420 GSM (Grams per Square Meter) for a durable and substantial feel.\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eStraight baggy fit for comfortable and versatile wear.\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eUnisex article suitable for a wide range of body types and style preferences.\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eBack pocket for convenient storage.\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eElasticated waist to adjust for a custom fit and added style.\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eSoft, breathable jersey fabric ensures comfort and airflow.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46853861638298,"sku":"bottoms","price":1799.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":46853861671066,"sku":"bottoms","price":1799.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":46853861703834,"sku":"bottoms","price":1799.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46853861736602,"sku":"bottoms","price":1799.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46853861769370,"sku":"bottoms","price":1799.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46853861802138,"sku":"bottoms","price":1799.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/IMG_5633_11zon.jpg?v=1768930731"},{"product_id":"black-basic-bottom","title":"BLACK BASIC BOTTOM","description":"\u003cp\u003e MODEL HEIGHT 5'10 AND WAIST SIZE 32 WEARING M BOTTOMS.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n420 GSM TAPED COTTON FLEECE\u003cbr\u003e\nCOMBED \u0026amp; BIO-WASHED FINISH\u003cbr\u003e\nSTRAIGHT BAGGY FIT\u003cbr\u003e\nJET BLACK MINIMAL DESIGN\u003cbr\u003e\nUNISEX ARTICLE [REFER TO SIZE CHART FOR ACCURATE MEASUREMENTS]. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCrafted from 420 GSM premium taped cotton fleece for a dense, structured feel with long-term durability.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStraight baggy silhouette delivers relaxed comfort with a modern streetwear edge.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eClean blank finish makes it easy to pair with graphic tees, hoodies, or elevated essentials.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eJet black tone offers a timeless, sharp look suitable for both casual and styled outfits.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTaped fleece construction adds structure while maintaining flexibility and everyday comfort.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePerfect for all seasons, offering warmth, breathability, and a premium heavyweight presence.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMachine wash the bottoms inside out with similar colors.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUse cold water to preserve fabric depth and finish.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTumble dry on low heat or air dry to maintain structure.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStore folded in a cool, dry place to retain shape.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e420 GSM taped fleece for a substantial premium feel.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStraight baggy fit for versatile, comfortable wear.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUnisex design suitable for multiple body types and styles.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMinimal blank aesthetic for effortless outfit pairing.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eElasticated waist for adjustable comfort and support.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAll-season fabric balance between warmth and breathability.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e","brand":"DRIPDRIP","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46881408647322,"sku":"BLINDDROP3","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"M","offer_id":46881408680090,"sku":"BLINDDROP3","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":46881408712858,"sku":"BLINDDROP3","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46881408745626,"sku":"BLINDDROP3","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46881408778394,"sku":"BLINDDROP3","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46881408811162,"sku":"BLINDDROP3","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00478copy_1__11zon.jpg?v=1772290631"},{"product_id":"regular-cropped-tee","title":"REGULAR CROPPED TEE - WHITE","description":"\u003cp\u003e240 GSM. Premium Fabric. Minimal Design. 100% Combed Cotton. Gender-Neutral. Regular-Fit Cropped Silhouette. Relaxed Waist. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis premium 240 GSM cropped T-shirt from Drip Studios is designed for effortless everyday wear. Crafted with a clean, minimal aesthetic, it features a regular fit with a relaxed waistline that offers comfort without compromising structure. The cropped length adds a modern edge, making it easy to style across casual and elevated looks. Made from combed and bio-washed cotton, this tee delivers a soft hand feel, breathability, and long-lasting durability. A versatile essential built for comfort, balance, and timeless appeal.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eProducts in lighter shades (such as white or off-white) are \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cstrong data-start=\"60\" data-end=\"99\"\u003enot eligible for return or exchange\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003e due to the high risk of stains, discoloration, or signs of use during handling or trial. Customers are advised to review product details carefully before placing an order for these colors.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the T-shirt inside out with similar colors. Use cold water to maintain fabric quality. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to avoid shrinkage. Store in a cool, dry place to preserve the fabric.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM fabric for a lightweight yet premium feel. Regular-fit cropped design with a relaxed waist for easy movement and comfort. Gender-neutral silhouette suitable for diverse body types. Soft, breathable combed cotton ensures all-day wearability. Bio-washed finish for enhanced durability a\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIPDRIP","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46881409106074,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":46881409138842,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1