003e\n\u003cli\u003eElasticated waist for adjustable comfort and everyday wear.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eBalanced fabric weight ideal for all-season use.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46885165072538,"sku":"Reign4","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"M","offer_id":46885165105306,"sku":"Reign4","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":46885165138074,"sku":"Reign4","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46885165170842,"sku":"Reign4","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46885165203610,"sku":"Reign4","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46885165236378,"sku":"Reign4","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00452copy_11zon.jpg?v=1772290145"},{"product_id":"black-polo","title":"BLACK POLO","description":"\u003cp\u003e220 GSM. Super Premium Matte Lycra Fabric. Refined Polo Construction. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed. Gender-Neutral. Tailored Regular Fit.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis super-premium 220 GSM polo T-shirt from Drip Studios is designed for those who appreciate quiet luxury in everyday essentials. Crafted from a refined matte lycra blend, the fabric offers a smooth, elevated finish with natural stretch for comfort and structure. The tailored regular fit delivers a sharp, composed silhouette, while the classic polo collar adds a touch of timeless sophistication.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCombed and bio-washed for exceptional softness and durability, this polo balances breathability, polish, and long-lasting performance. Built to transition seamlessly from relaxed settings to elevated occasions, it stands as a modern wardrobe staple defined by restraint, precision, and premium craftsmanship.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003