le for everyday wear. Excellent stretch and recovery for long-term shape retention. Made in India with a focus on quality craftsmanship.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIPDRIP","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47079282835610,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1499.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"M","offer_id":47079282868378,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1499.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"L","offer_id":47079282901146,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1499.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47079282933914,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1499.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00065copy_11zon.jpg?v=1771440076"},{"product_id":"henley-offwhite","title":"HENLEY - OFF-WHITE","description":"\u003cp\u003eMODEL HEIGHT 5'9\" WEARING M SIZE\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e220 GSM. Hefty Cotton Fabric. Slim Fit Body-Hugging Silhouette. 96% Cotton \u0026amp; 4% Spandex. Gender-Neutral. Made in India.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis premium 220 GSM slim-fit T-shirt is designed to elevate everyday essentials with a refined, body-hugging silhouette. Crafted from a luxurious blend of 96% cotton and 4% spandex, it offers the perfect balance of softness, stretch, and structure for all-day comfort. The hefty cotton fabric delivers a smooth, premium hand feel while maintaining breathability and shape retention. Thoughtfully made in India, this tee is built to move with you—enhancing your style with clean lines, superior fit, and lasting quality.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eProducts in lighter shades (such as white or off-white) are \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cstrong data-start=\"60\" data-end=\"99\"\u003enot eligible for return or exchange\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003e due to the high risk of stains, discoloration, or signs of use during handling or trial. Customers are advised to review product details carefully before placing an order f