d silhouette designed for modern everyday wear. Classic ringer neckline and sleeve contrast detailing. Minimal blank design for versatile styling. Gender-neutral construction suitable for multiple body types. Combed and bio-washed cotton for enhanced softness, breathability, and durability.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIPDRIP","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47546240663706,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":47546240696474,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":47546240729242,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47546240762010,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00363copy_11zon.jpg?v=1772787384"},{"product_id":"raglan-cropped-tee-wine","title":"RAGLAN CROPPED TEE - WINE","description":"\u003cp\u003eMODEL HEIGHT 5'9\" WEARING M SIZE\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM. Premium French Terry Cotton. Cropped Silhouette with Raglan Full Sleeves. Minimal Design. Gender-Neutral. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis cropped 240 GSM full-sleeve T-shirt from Drip Studios is crafted for a clean, super-decent everyday look. Designed with raglan sleeves, it offers a relaxed shoulder fit and effortless movement, while the cropped length adds a modern, balanced silhouette. Made from premium French terry cotton, this tee delivers softness, breathability, and lasting comfort. With its basic, minimal aesthetic and refined finish, it’s a versatile essential that pairs easily with any wardrobe for understated style.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the T-shirt inside out with similar colors. Use cold water to preserve fabric quality. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage. Store in a cool, dry place